highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 214 weeks straight.
Juice WRLD has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lucid Dreams” is the highest at #80.
“What’s Next” by Drake is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Just the Way You Are” by Bruno Mars is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 29 spots at #138.
